      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE DEVIL IN HER (1) was a very sharp winner two back at a mile before another good effort up in grade at Caulfield when closing well off a slow speed. Another rise in trip will suit perfectly now for the in-form yard. TIMEONLEES (6) is in great form, dominant at Echuca last time on very heavy going but good behind a progressive one at Donald prior. She gets in very light after the claim and can give a bold sight again. HARSH (2) comes over from Adelaide in good form, a dominant winner two back before chasing home the handy Wudzz which is form that stacks up over here. Go close. ZEYNO (7) was well in contention behind a handy one who was well backed in town last start. Didn't fire there but can bounce back. REALIKA (4) got home well here last time and is in the mix.",
